[30;1m855 | [0m[35m    def scale_height(self, factor: float) -> MTextEditor:[0m
[30;1m856 | [0m[35m        """Scale the text height by a `factor`. This scaling will accumulate,[0m

[30;1m154 | [0m[35m#[0m
[30;1m155 | [0m[35m# A bounded INSERT needs a SEQEND to be valid at export if there are attached[0m
[30;1m156 | [0m[35m# ATTRIB entities, but the LinkedEntities.post_bind_hook() method creates[0m
[30;1m157 | [0m[35m# always a new SEQEND after binding the INSERT entity to a document.[0m
[30;1m158 | [0m[35m#[0m

[30;1m7 | [0m[35mA list of :class:`~ezdxf.lldxf.types.DXFTag`, inherits from Python standard list.[0m
[30;1m8 | [0m[35mUnlike the statement in the DXF Reference "Do not write programs that rely on[0m
[30;1m9 | [0m[35mthe order given here", tag order is sometimes essential and some group codes[0m
[30;1m10 | [0m[35mmay appear multiples times in one entity. At the worst case[0m
[30;1m11 | [0m[35m(:class:`~ezdxf.entities.material.Material`: normal map shares group codes with[0m
[30;1m12 | [0m[35mdiffuse map) using same group codes with different meanings.[0m
